quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,Ulon meusumpah lon ngon uroe nyan Kiamat yoh nyan hebat sileupah
  75,2,Ulon meusumpah ngon napsu nyang got Meunyo hana got jikheun nyan salah
  75,3,Peue nyang jisangka le manusia Hana kuasa kamoe that leupah Tuleung jih han ek Kamoe peusapat
  75,4,Nyang leubeh lom brat ek Kamoe ulah Ujong jaroe jih ek meupeusaban
  75,5,Teutapi insan napsu keu salah Napsu jimaksiet hana jipiyoh
  75,6,Jikheun pajan troh peue nyang tapeugah Uroe kiamat pajan troh teuka
  75,7,‘Oh teuglong mata jih peue jipeugah
  75,8,Watee ka gadoh cahaya buleun
  75,9,Meunan pih buleuen geupinah sudah Ngon mata uroe jih geupeusapat
  75,10,Watee nyan meuhat seungap dum babah Nyang na jeuet jikheun ho takeumeung pluen; Gata nyoe bandum cit ka Iheuh salah
  75,11,Tapi hana le jalan rot taplueng
  75,12,Teutap uroe nyan keudeh bak Allah
  75,13,Geubri thee bandum bak manusia Uroe nyan teuma dumpeue geupeugah Nyang ka jipubuet got goh jipubuet
  75,14,Atra nyan nyang buet droe jieu sudah Droejih keu saksi sit deuh jikalon
  75,15,Bah le beu jikheun jih hana salah
  75,16,Bek tagrak dilee nyan lidah gata Takeumeung baca bagah that leupah
  75,17,Kamoe peusapat teuma meubaca
  75,18,‘Oh kamoe baca tatiree bagah
  75,19,Lheuh nyan meukeusud jih kamoe peutrang
  75,20,Tapi gata dum laen that ulah Galak teuh that-that keu seunang donya
  75,21,Akhirat teuma ka roh takeubah
  75,22,Uroe nyan teuma na muka nyang gleh
  75,23,Jieu Tuhan jih seunang jih leupah
  75,24,Teuma uroe nyan na muka nyang krot
  75,25,Akan geutuntut yakin jih sudah Meuhajat that jih jikeumeung gisa
  75,26,Tapi nyawong ka bak uram lidah Meu ka troh nyawong keunan bak reukueng
  75,27,Laju geutanyong soe keumeung rajah
  75,28,Jiyakin yoh nyan jih nyan ka meucre
  75,29,Hana jalan le soe keumeung peuglah Beuteh ngon beuteh meutindeh lapeh
  75,30,Bak puteh keudeh bandum meulangkah